Class TransportIndexDeleteAction

          • org.elasticsearch.action.delete.TransportIndexDeleteAction

  • public class TransportIndexDeleteAction
extends TransportIndexReplicationOperationAction<org.elasticsearch.action.delete.IndexDeleteRequest,IndexDeleteResponse,ShardDeleteRequest,ShardDeleteRequest,ShardDeleteResponse>
    Internal transport action that broadcasts a delete request to all of the shards that belongs to an index. Used when routing is required but not specified within the delete request.
